Pope Francis’ historic talk to Congress live at
6:20am on Thursday, September 24 at Christ Our
Hope Parish (1902 2nd Ave). Doors open at
6:00am, and Mass will follow the talk.</p>
<p><b>SABBATH: UNPLUGGING FROM THE CULTURE OF
NOW</b>. Join us for a three evenings of reflection in
the midst of your busy life! Facilitated by Rosanne
Michaels and Tom Frasene, this series will discuss
how we can make room for God and what the role
of the Christian is in today’s restless, consumer
society. Join us on Wednesdays, September 30,
October 14, and October 28, 7pm-9:15pm, in the
Parish Outreach Center (907 Columbia St.).</p>
