and young adults are eligible for deferred action and
work authorization. We can help you figure out if you
are eligible and help you through the entire application
process. <i>Information</i>, 
<a href="mailto:ctrigg@stjames-cathedral.org?subject=Are You a Dreamer?">
Christine Trigg</a>, Immigrant Legal
